name: Captain Amelia (treasure planet) Disney By YeiyeiArt
description:
Captain Amelia is a well-known character from treasure planet. To create the Lora, a meticulously selected and refined DataSet was used to achieve a versatile and flexible model. So that it adapts perfectly to styles and models. It also works in 3D. Use the keyword “(AmeliaCapWaifu:1)” for greater precision, and I also recommend using the keywords “(blue uniform, thighhighs, thigh boots, gloves, hat, epaulettes, pants), to invoke her characteristic outfits. If you want to change her outfit, I recommend lowering the weight of the Lora between “1.0 - 0.6” for greater flexibility, try it out and have fun. Remember to leave a Review with an image if you liked it and comment!! HAVE FUN :D
